0d8c9df31c1b89.png\" width=\"1537\" alt=\"Optimize headlines and taglines\"></noscript></p>\n<p>Your landing pages have to be very clear about your product and attract your visitor’s attention from the start. People’s attention span is just about <a href=\"http://www.quicksprout.com/2013/08/08/this-is-your-brain-on-visualization/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">8 - 9 seconds,</a> so you have to make sure you tell all the important stuff first and tell it as fast as possible to get more clicks, sales, and conversions.</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-keep-all-important-information-above-the-fold\"><a href=\"#2-keep-all-important-information-above-the-fold\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>2. Keep all important information above the fold</h2>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1537 671' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-f66767634f05e8e822c28f3920cb5830'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-f66767634f05e8e822c28f3920cb5830)' width='1537' height='671' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAAcCAYAAADRJblSAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAMRklEQVRYw%2bVYaWxc1RU2qoBKpaKCNmrVP/3RUqSqaSGlgNoiRAkQkjheIGELBAJkIfESb3E2Z2ugDilxFmcjiRPixE5iO3Zie7yMx7PYHo/3fZsZj8eefd7si5eZ%2bXre84zt2AY5VVUp9Eqf7n137n1vznfP/c65NyzssSeejfxbkXTTcgWSImy%2bhFUMWCRGWL6v8CdHOlkbddR%2bJOzhRUsQ9tivsWRxWiA12ottq0z/dwQEyAsCf1q8F0RA4H9FwH/vG8wsWGa1J5%2bnv8csjICEVfO9fIGIZJAUabkLs40OtUO/cYhk51rmIOlbwI1njQsa%2bF1jJkmYnwDaAr9BkIAZW2CaRXbiJJhZoL5wC7axWGlBPIsVFsQtZxC7jEEMYeur1H6dmTJ6psbEr6TfX2NoziTiXrfQWMucOvSumWD72N/iV9iniJzqX2YO1tNjQgtK9RwCxh94/En/M4v3IzVq0gNCbMUtZw2b4T70keSo4MrQmKQoBsnRDFLeYJC6hsGudxns%2b5DBPzYw%2bDLWhqOJdmTutCF9i41Iml790J89QmM668cgvuNBdaEbsionGqrcqOe70CDwcLWMnpuqvWgRj6FZNMrVTUIvpJ