b0f0ae02.png\" width=\"1537\" alt=\"Different payment options\"></noscript></p>\n<p>Nowadays, landing pages needs to support the most common payment options. Many of your visitors might abandon their transactions if their preferred payment option isn’t or appears not to be available.</p>\n<h2 id=\"4-choosing-monthly-vs-annual-subscriptions\"><a href=\"#4-choosing-monthly-vs-annual-subscriptions\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>4. Choosing Monthly vs Annual Subscriptions</h2>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1537 671' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-13b94dfda3d1398730c2cd3963a67edc'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-13b94dfda3d1398730c2cd3963a67edc)' width='1537' height='671' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAAcCAYAAADRJblSAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAJNElEQVRYw91ZCVBV1xl%2bponJtHG0LsS202k7NcZpWqdxbTtJjEZsjYg8UaN1jZ0mcakiCALKoiSpmrqAokaIGwpUrCKEqogTSWoUkFLFxIVF2Xk83v7ufdu95%2bs5576HD3mgotJJ78zH%2bc95/7n//b/7n//856JS9R86Vv1azqUlU6oQHmSUwqbpwLA6SI%2bI6XqE9yCYPWbXY/8JQY5QW5iNJio/r3rWbyRU/Ydg5PA4EhVsQ%2bg0LVdcFaDDsomtWObvxsQnCC8bq6bqnjQJHQggNArIqOHxoASQsCAtQqbo8Nf3jTj7dxFnMh4R6YIC3hfc8K2bnyki4U8Gbr8nI6AdAavVyts4stUK3xdxw1v27ntf8gPI7a/UDWZuP3x6jy6BF%2bEmAIyA5ZN0SPvYwh9IchHIEoXMZBminQFwOZ0gssRb5pDT4aR6LjjsDoiCDTabAzb6i7WiGtZbVbBRbkTdHYgtN2CjU0TRSee6%2bH3Z/V0uhbxP4szcfk8S4Ow1YJg8evgGRE1XIsCbAFkmIER5OPqcsGtv0D%2b30Wpw4GalFjq9gLKrjbytrTdCEBwUFv6ObXEJ0A/%2bCfQ//gWEmFmQTrwI1%2bGBkItCqMNOOF0uJW4I4XbYtTe%2bhwl4bvBYqPr%2bCMNfXiNHB9tpBGh9EuAhoaHqJi4cTcS23V8hakM%2bPtxyHiFReaisbkXQ3HQUldRyPaGsHA1vvwPtxKnQTA6AMeR16NKnwJwzHuasMbA3XgJ3n8g%2bCFCWgGdHepzoQMB3Bv5qwesjE8sX%%2bIAbDUVNHUcgf36bjhM9bA7Cc8DHXJAnLILsFwUFng3dEOZ7IGn79W2Q2D7lumEBtJ7BrG%2bviMBVDgVPcPJFLokwCXJ